<bibRefCitation author="Paula, A. C. M. &amp; Moresco, G. A. &amp; Bortolini, J. C. &amp; Jati, J. &amp; Reis, L. M. &amp; Rodrigues, L. C." box="[931,1128,1922,1948]" pageId="10" pageNumber="238" pagination="417 - 431" refId="ref8763" refString="Paula, A. C. M., Moresco, G. A., Bortolini, J. C., Jati, J., Reis, L. M. &amp; Rodrigues, L. C. (2014) Os generos Staurastrum, Staurodesmus e Xanthidium em uma lagoa de inundacao, planicie de inundacao do alto rio Parana, Brasil. Iheringia 69 (2): 417 - 431." type="journal article" year="2014">
Paula 
<emphasis box="[1003,1060,1922,1948]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="238">et al.</emphasis>
2014
</bibRefCitation>
), Southeast (
<bibRefCitation author="Borgesen, F." box="[1273,1447,1922,1948]" pageId="10" pageNumber="238" pagination="24 - 53" refId="ref7273" refString="Borgesen, F. (1891) Symbolae ad floram Brasiliae centralis cognoscendam. Edit. Eug. Warming. Particula XXXIV. Videnskabelige meddelelser fra den Naturhistoriske forening i Kjobenhavn 1890: 24 - 53." type="journal article" year="1891">Børgesen 1891</bibRefCitation>
